  10 Jan 2004: Paul Varner <paul@varnerfamily.org>
  Fixed ebuild problems indicated by repoman

*kernelmod-rebuild-0.2.1 (09 Jan 2004)

  09 Jan 2004: Paul Varner <paul@varnerfamily.org> kernelmod-rebuild,
  kernelmod-rebuild-0.2.1:
  Fixed bug with --package-names not working correctly

*kernelmod-rebuild-0.2 (22 Dec 2003)

  22 Dec 2003: Paul Varner <paul@varnerfamily.org> kernelmod-rebuild,
  kernelmod-rebuild-0.2:
  Verison bump.

*kernelmod-rebuild-0.2_pre4 (17 Dec 2003)

  17 Dec 2003: Paul Varner <paul@varnerfamily.org> kernelmod-rebuild,
  kernelmod-rebuild-0.2_pre4:
  Fix spelling and formatting errors.
  Added --ordered-rebuild option

*kernelmod-rebuild-0.2_pre3 (16 Dec 2003)

  16 Dec 2003: Paul Varner <paul@varnerfamily.org> kernelmod-rebuild,
  kernelmod-rebuild-0.2_pre3:
  Minor bug fixes.  Added --no-color & --ignore options.  Ignore 
  temporary files older than one day.
  Changed config file from /etc/conf.d/kernemod-rebuild to
  /etc/kernelmod-rebuild.conf.

*kernelmod-rebuild-0.2_pre2 (16 Dec 2003)

  16 Dec 2003: Paul Varner <paul@varnerfamily.org> kernelmod-rebuild,
  kernelmod-rebuild-0.2_pre2:
  Added support for /etc/conf.d/kernemod-rebuild to blacklist packages
  and check non-standard directories

*kernelmod-rebuild-0.2_pre1 (09 Dec 2003)

  09 Dec 2003: Paul Varner <paul@varnerfamily.org> kernelmod-rebuild,
  kernelmod-rebuild-0.2_pre1:
  Added --smart-rebuild option

*kernelmod-rebuild-0.1 (02 Dec 2003)

  02 Dec 2003; Paul Varner <paul@varnerfamily.org> kernelmod-rebuild,
  kernelmod-rebuild-0.1.ebuild :
  Initial build/release.

